{"tid":1745002,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《寸土必爭》我地要「建制、落選」, 唔係要「血債票償」!","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T01:26:07.000Z","uid":4857,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d41181089a9860cd99c0cd85b4c528412b63c570","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"首先, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血債唔係票可以償到! 只有真雙普選可以慰義士在天之靈!<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42ixeMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42ixeMA.jpg&h=8cdf2b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日愈黎愈多<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分化撚</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最常見既講法係<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民主黨點衰/要投白票</span></strong></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">臭蟲論</span></span>, 用<del>建制衰泛民都衰所以無分別</del>洗我地腦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住, 我地而家係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>令建制落選</strong></span>, 唔係要「血債票償」!<br />\n<br />\n仲未下定決心投票既巴打們要明白, 今日建制造票造到咁, 如果我地都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以令建制落選, 民主黨可以唔驚咩</span></span>? 我地連建制都趕得走, 唔通到時泛民唔聽話佢又能夠連任? 呢件事唔單止係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令建制落選</span></strong>, 仲係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告泛民</span></strong>, 票係我地手!<br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制、落選</span></span>！"},{"pid":"ce1dc68451bd4332a9a25b54a85d3b0e81e8c973","tid":1745002,"uid":144084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n全港團結絕殺保皇黨!!!"},{"pid":"dba0af09c3e5e5c6e6afb36749ceadba8da7c2a0","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1dc68451bd4332a9a25b54a85d3b0e81e8c973","tid":1745002,"uid":144084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n全港團結絕殺保皇黨!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打, 一齊推上去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c24c6e53dcd1a5219476b5d257a7912b25c9b2","tid":1745002,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"寧願投個唔做野既都唔要賣港區議員"},{"pid":"17f55536235f4acc24e4f36b570fd3865b8d50b7","tid":1745002,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:22:52.000Z","msg":"總之佢哋要輸"},{"pid":"2411938caa6beb79c8ccc0a98e5a7e86b9d6013e","tid":1745002,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:23:44.000Z","msg":"全民落區唱衰保皇黨!<br />\n<br />\n不要只在連登開戰!"},{"pid":"4ae2133daefca2ef95cb212483cf81839b251eeb","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08c24c6e53dcd1a5219476b5d257a7912b25c9b2","tid":1745002,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"寧願投個唔做野既都唔要賣港區議員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"講真, 迫D唔做野既高票當選, 要佢地明白自己D票點黎, 佢地自然就會上力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b71375b310d74f480420a