"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d3f954e3d9fb22e2b97b428a6c0ac79f36ed65","tid":1745002,"uid":223353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50c417df9b77d3d1ee607128ca483d331fde465e","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd33610d42400317b545a1aa909992e4fd67bf42","tid":1745002,"uid":223353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZDYbgd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZDYbgd.jpg&h=9dacf507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解決咁大量種票先得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"呢D最好補多個EMAIL比選管會, 要正式回覆就無得唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"叫好多港豬做埋呢步 簡直難過登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9550d1aa3c8f63b46cfe0072c906c176c25c50","tid":1745002,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=d9de9dd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838572f2db8efacff855736a496a006f89db9ff4","tid":1745002,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"星期日投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3987cded0d6a3b0744ec2233110dad80b7e2c79b","tid":1745002,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"保皇"},{"pid":"873c82afaae824df98019fecfbc2e1c9f8fa2f9d","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d3f954e3d9fb22e2b97b428a6c0ac79f36ed65","tid":1745002,"uid":223353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50c417df9b77d3d1ee607128ca483d331fde465e","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd33610d42400317b545a1aa909992e4fd67bf42","tid":1745002,"uid":223353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZDYbgd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZDYbgd.jpg&h=9dacf507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解決咁大量種票先得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"呢D最好補多個EMAIL比選管會, 要正式回覆就無得唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"叫好多港豬做埋呢步 簡直難過登天<img sr