hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">臭蟲論</span></span>, 用<del>建制衰泛民都衰所以無分別</del>洗我地腦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住, 我地而家係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>令建制落選</strong></span>, 唔係要「血債票償」!<br />\n<br />\n仲未下定決心投票既巴打們要明白, 今日建制造票造到咁, 如果我地都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以令建制落選, 民主黨可以唔驚咩</span></span>? 我地連建制都趕得走, 唔通到時泛民唔聽話佢又能夠連任? 呢件事唔單止係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令建制落選</span></strong>, 仲係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告泛民</span></strong>, 票係我地手!<br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制、落選</span></span>！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"建你老母制，保皇狗啊！！！"},{"pid":"734d7b5462932115ada5270c7673b61cb19037e0","tid":1745002,"uid":263475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1de20fa1e6617d3ae3a8370c8bb52acf9cbf37a","tid":1745002,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"好撚煩呀<br />\n要拉票一係落區<br />\n一係就喺深藍討論區拉啦<br />\n喺連登拉把撚咩"},{"pid":"48f7837a00da668ce04198d552d66cec0fc29bd8","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb275ea9c9a4d9cb7bcb32907bf5ce355bb95207","tid":1745002,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d41181089a9860cd99c0cd85b4c528412b63c570","tid":1745002,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"首先, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血債唔係票可以償到! 只有真雙普選可以慰義士在天之靈!<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42ixeMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42ixeMA.jpg&h=8cdf2b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日愈黎愈多<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分化撚</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最常見既講法係<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民主黨點衰/要投白票</span></strong></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">臭蟲論</span></span>, 用<del>建制衰泛民都衰所以無分別</del>洗我地腦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住, 我地而家係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>令建制落選</strong></span>, 唔係要「血債票償」!<br />\n<br />\n仲未下定決心投票既巴打們要明白, 今日建制造票造到咁, 如果我地都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以令建制落選, 民主黨可以唔驚咩</span></span>? 我地連建制都趕得走, 唔通到時泛民唔聽話佢又能夠連任? 呢件事唔單止係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令建制落選</span></strong>, 仲係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告泛民</span></strong>, 票係我地手!<br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制、落選</span></span>！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"建你老母制，保皇狗啊！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你岩, 我錯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">保皇、落選！</span></span